  "remarks": "Reportedly deceased in June 2020. Head of The Organization of Al-Qaida in the Islamic Maghreb (QE.T.14.01.). Sentenced in absentia to life imprisonment in Algeria on 21 March 2007. Father’s name is Rabah Droukdel. Mother’s name is Z’hour Zdigha.Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2253 (2015) was concluded on 21 Feb. 2019. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2610 (2021) was concluded on 8 November 2022.; Listing: Listed on 27 August 2007 (amended on 7 April 2008, 13 Dec. 2011, 1 May 2019, 2 February 2023)",
